but i can’t ask for that 
because we are not one...

sometimes i get insecure

and it would feel good

to hear him say nice things

but i can’t ask for that

because we are not one


i wish we would go on dates

i’m in need of romancing

to feel warmth in my chest

but i can’t ask for that

because we are not one

summary: Hey! I finished a new piece. These are pieces I am making from the maps I used from my my hike of the Pyrenees mountains.  I'm...
body:
Hey! I finished a new piece. These are pieces I am making from the maps I used from my my hike of the Pyrenees mountains. I’m trying to raise funds for my next hike which will be of the Pacifi Crest Trail. A description of the piece is below. Its 35$, shipping included, and it’s on my big cartel which is linked. Many thanks for the support!

This is my moniker done on a piece of map that I used on my walk across the Spanish Pyrenees. This map was very special to me because it was my guide, my safety and comfort. One of my greatest comforts on the trail. It came with me the entire trip and to me holds some of the trip within it, if not In spirit at least in the dirt, food, sweat, rain or whatever got on it. I will be making more of these on other maps that I used for the trip. This piece is 17cm by 11.5 cm. The moniker was done with paint markers. Shipping is included.
